OL,3,CJudge set to pass verdict after trial
OL,4,Cof man who burned Koran
OL,6,FA judge is set to pass verdict after
OL,7,Fthe trial of a man who burned a Koran
OL,8,Foutside the Turkish consulate in
OL,9,FLondon.
OL,11,FHamit Coskun, 50, shouted "f***
OL,12,FIslam", "Islam is religion of
OL,13,Fterrorism" and "Koran is burning" as
OL,14,Fhe held the flaming Islamic text aloft
OL,15,Fin Rutland Gardens, Knightsbridge,
OL,16,FLondon, on February 13, Westminster
OL,17,FMagistrates' Court heard last week.
