OL,3,CJudge set to pass verdict after trial
OL,4,Cof man who burned Koran
OL,6,FTurkey-born Coskun, who is half
OL,7,FKurdish and half Armenian, travelled
OL,8,Ffrom his home in the Midlands and set
OL,9,Ffire to the Koran at around 2pm, the
OL,10,Fcourt heard.
OL,12,FIn footage captured on a mobile phone
OL,13,Fby a passerby that was shown to the
OL,14,Fcourt, a man approached and asked
OL,15,FCoskun why he was burning a copy of
OL,16,Fthe Koran.
OL,18,FCoskun can be heard making a reference
OL,19,Fto "terrorist" and the man called the
OL,20,Fdefendant "a f****** idiot".
