OL,4,Cof man who burned Koran
OL,6,FThe man approached him allegedly
OL,7,Fholding a knife or bladed article and
OL,8,Fappeared to slash out at him, the
OL,9,Fcourt heard.
OL,11,FThe footage appeared to show Coskun
OL,12,Fback away and use the burning Koran to
OL,13,Fdeflect the attacker, who is alleged
OL,14,Fto have slashed out at him again.
OL,16,FThe man chased Coskun, and the
OL,17,Fdefendant stumbled forward and fell to
OL,18,Fthe ground, dropping the Koran, the
OL,19,Ffootage showed.
