OL,3,CJudge set to pass verdict after trial
OL,4,Cof man who burned Koran
OL,6,FCoskun was spat at and kicked by the
OL,7,Fman, the court heard.
OL,9,FThe man said: "Burning the Koran? It's
OL,10,Fmy religion, you don't burn the Koran."
OL,12,FCoskun had posted on social media that
OL,13,Fhe was protesting against the
OL,14,F"Islamist government" of Turkish
OL,15,FPresident Recep Tayyip Erdogan who the
OL,16,Fdefendant allegedly said "has made
OL,17,FTurkey a base for radical Islamists
OL,18,Fand is trying to establish a Sharia
OL,19,Fregime", prosecutors said.
