OL,6,FThe defendant, who is an atheist,
OL,7,Fbelieves that he protested peacefully
OL,8,Fand burning the Koran amounted to
OL,9,Ffreedom of expression, the court heard.
OL,11,FHis legal fees are being paid for by
OL,12,Fthe Free Speech Union and the National
OL,13,FSecular Society (NSS).
OL,15,FDistrict Judge John McGarva will pass
OL,16,Fverdict at the same court on Monday.
